   about IAC Partners

   About us

Improve your competitiveness

   IAC Partners is a strategy consulting firm renowned for its technical
   and operational expertise.

   Building on more than 30 years of experience, IAC Partners serves its
   clients through 4 core Practices: Product Excellence &
   Development, Procurement & Supply Chain, Digital Transformation &
   Enabling Technology and Organization & Change.

   IAC Partners, based in Paris, Lyon, Düsseldorf, Chicago and Singapore,
   serves its clients, Mid-Caps or Large International Groups on all
   continents while understanding their local needs
   Read more about it

