   Customer Testimonial

     Technical Direction, Thales The contribution of the firm has been
     decisive to question certainties, challenge teams in their choice,
     identify new technical and supply chain solutions.

     Technical Direction, Zodiac Aerospace Thanks to their team's
     experience, IAC was able to understand the subject, mobilize the
     teams internally and achieve mission's objectives within the
     expected deadlines.

     Technical Direction, Plastic Omnium They allowed us through their
     analytical and back office methods to broaden the spectrum of our
     supplier panel for new components in a time frame that we were
     unable to respect with our internal resources and methods.

     Purchasing Management, SEB The methodology used and the quality of
     the speakers allowed us to overcome all the difficulties of this
     project to make it a success.

     Technical Direction, Schneider Electric IAC quickly provides a
     strong synthesis and analysis capability that accelerates projects.

     R&D Direction, BÉABA IAC’s coaching has contributed positively to
     mastering our development and its delicate planning and cost
     aspects. The implementation of methods and procedures of analysis
     piloted by IAC has enriched our thinking and allowed us to select
     with more certainty the technological choices and suppliers. In
     today’s industrial world, the openness given by IAC and the
     effective commitment of their team is an undeniable project asset.

     Technical Direction, France Fermetures Systematic analysis of the
     product and practices around the product has allowed us to generate
     significant gains while equipping ourselves with a product that
     better responds to its market.

     Product Management, Alstom The reduction in overall cost has
     exceeded the initial assessment which seemed ambitious.

     General Management, Groupe Compin Whatever the size and level of
     complexity of an enterprise or project, their consultants know how
     to adapt to it in order to lead our teams to the best results.

     Industrial Management, Faiveley transport The presentation of the
     results has generated considerable interest which has been widely
     used to enrich the analysis of the industrialisation process at all
     levels of the Business Unit.

     Technical Direction, Salomon This is a success. Their team was able
     to challenge and motivate teams despite a challenging environment.

     Industrial Operations Division, SEB Within Groupe SEB, we have had
     the opportunity to involve the company in numerous major engineering
     projects. We particularly appreciated their ability to move lines
     and embark our teams from strategic marketing, to industrial
     operations, through all aspects of product creation.

     Energy and Boiler Director, EIFFAGE MÉTAL For EIFFAGE MÉTAL,
     unfamiliar with the use of consultants in operational process
     improvement, this assignment was of strategic importance beyond the
     project's objectives. IAC's offer reassured us by its transparency
     and its adequacy to our needs. The execution met our expectations,
     succeeding the human challenge, which was to secure the commitment
     of the project's operational staff. IAC also participated in
     meetings with our client, helping to secure their trust.

